{"title_page": "1998 NASCAR Winston Cup Series", "text_new": "{{short description|50th season of NASCAR stock-car racing}}\n{{Motorsport season\n|series = NASCAR Winston Cup Series\n|link = NASCAR Winston Cup Series\n|year = 1998\n}}\n[[File:Jeff Gordon 1998 by Darryl Moran.jpg|thumb|The 1998 Winston Cup Champion Jeff Gordon. It was Gordon's third championship in four years.]]\n[[File:Mark martin Pocono June 98.jpeg|thumb|[[Mark Martin]] finished second behind Gordon by 364 points]]\n[[File:Dale Jarrett 1997.jpg|thumb|[[Dale Jarrett]] finished third in the championship]]\n\nThe '''1998 NASCAR Winston Cup Series season''' was the 50th season of [[Sprint Cup Series|professional]] [[stock car racing]] in the United States and the 27th modern-era cup series. The season included 33 races and three exhibition races, beginning with the [[1998 Daytona 500|Daytona 500]] at [[Daytona International Speedway]] and ending with the [[NAPA 500]] at [[Atlanta Motor Speedway]]. [[Jeff Gordon]] won the Driver's Championship, the third of his career and his third in the last four seasons.\n\n1998 was the last season without either NASCAR Legends: [[Tony Stewart]] until [[2017 Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series|2017]], and [[Dale Earnhardt Jr.|Dale Earnhardt Jr]] until [[2018 Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series|2018]].\n\n==Teams and drivers==\n\n===Complete schedule===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|+\n|-\n!Manufacturer\n!Team\n!{{Tooltip|No.|Car number}}\n!Race Driver\n!Crew Chief\n|-\n! rowspan=\"39\" | [[Chevrolet]]\n| rowspan=\"9\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[American Equipment Racing]]'''\n| rowspan=\"9\" |96\n| [[David Green (racing driver)|David Green]] <small>{{Tooltip|12|1-12}}</small>\n| rowspan=\"9\" | Sammy Johns\n|-\n| [[Kevin Lepage]] '''(R)''' <small>{{Tooltip|1|13}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Hut Stricklin]] <small>{{Tooltip|8|14-15, 17-19, 21-22, 24}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Robby Gordon]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|16}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Ron Fellows]] <small>{{Tooltip|2|20, 23}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Ted Musgrave]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|25}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Morgan Shepherd]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|26}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Mike Bliss]] <small>{{Tooltip|2|27, 31}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Steve Grissom]] <small>{{Tooltip|5|28-30, 32-33}}</small>\n|-\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[Andy Petree Racing]]'''\n|33\n| [[Ken Schrader]]\n| [[Andy Petree]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[Dale Earnhardt, Inc.]]'''\n| rowspan=\"4\" |1\n| [[Steve Park]] '''(R)''' <small>{{Tooltip|18|1-3, 19-33}}</small>\n| rowspan=\"4\" | Phillipe Lopez\n|-\n| [[Phil Parsons]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|4}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Ron Hornaday, Jr.]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|5}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Darrell Waltrip]] <small>{{Tooltip|13|6-18}}</small>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[Hendrick Motorsports]]'''\n|5\n| [[Terry Labonte]]\n| Andy Graves\n|-\n|24\n| [[Jeff Gordon]]\n| [[Ray Evernham]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |50\n| [[Ricky Craven]] <small>{{Tooltip|8|1-4, 17-20}}</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Tony Furr\n|-\n| [[Randy LaJoie]] <small>{{Tooltip|9|5-13}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Wally Dallenbach, Jr.]] <small>{{Tooltip|16|14-16, 21-33}}</small>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[Larry Hedrick Motorsports]]'''\n| rowspan=\"3\" |41\n| [[Steve Grissom]] <small>{{Tooltip|26|1-26}}</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Tim Brewer]]\n|-\n| [[David Green (racing driver)|David Green]] <small>{{Tooltip|5|27-28, 31-33}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Rick Wilson (racing driver)|Rick Wilson]] <small>{{Tooltip|2|29-30}}</small>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\" |'''[[LJ Racing]]'''\n| rowspan=\"5\" |91\n| [[Kevin Lepage]] '''(R)''' <small>{{Tooltip|15|1-15}}</small>\n| rowspan=\"5\" | Doug Richert\n|-\n| [[Tommy Kendall]] <small>{{Tooltip|1|16}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Andy Hillenburg]] <small>{{Tooltip|3|17, 29-30}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Morgan Shepherd]] <small>{{Tooltip|7|18-24}}</small>\n|-\n| [[Todd Bodine]] <small>{{Tooltip|7|25-28, 31-33}}</small>\n|-\n| style